{"tid":1537822,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"!!! 行動post!!! 9月6號！","createTime":"2019-09-04T05:15:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-05T13:52:12.000Z","uid":69503,"like":35,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"3a9a3ea2e93c762d41c13e6ec15477f1dbcb1dbd","tid":1537822,"uid":69503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T05:15:58.000Z","msg":"《請轉貼》<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><em><span style=\"color: red;\">9月6號，全民戴裝日</span></em></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n目的係提醒大家行街坐車都會隨時被襲擊，扑頭、噴椒、或身處毒霧環境，所以要戴上防具作象徵，靜默地抗議。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以下幾點提議比番大家:<br />\n1. 番學番工放工時間做，越多人做效果越好，人多亦唔易比人check身份證<br />\n2. 行街坐車行商場都戴住，唔使怕奇怪，因為更無理既事日日都發生緊<br />\n3. 番工裝扮未必帶到頭盔，但唔戴都帶住，作為一個象徵，又或者只帶口罩眼罩<br />\n4. 真勇武就小心，比人check身份證留record就麻煩<br />\n5. 只帶防具，只係要保護自己，唔好有其他可疑裝備<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">當人人都有頭盔口罩係身既時候，就可以淡化帶gear本身既奇怪，保護大家，亦比一份支持勇武。</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gqTNDGu.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgqTNDGu.gif&h=c04fb002&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c49198333ed869edfb9b2a5bc3c9f642c3ab136b","tid":1537822,"uid":123991,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T05:16:04.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n烏克蘭, 法國等其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮, 唔割但要小心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外可參考唔揸春袋揸輸精管方法: <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n [行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3e051e0b143e5c53ae5c4185f6f9b814ab0c14d3","tid":1537822,"uid":250654,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T05:20:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9f9QBut.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9f9QBut.jpg&h=c6f9cab3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/noVgw2O.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnoVgw2O.png&h=08a0b3a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>全民戴口罩</strong></span>"},{"pid":"c7b99c7f7c021d1456eed5f2cd30631f5cf107c7","tid":1537822,"uid":69503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T05:25:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"26d9e3c54c00a7f43e9cd454c1627b766ca34661","tid":1537822,"uid":69503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T05:25:59.000Z","msg":"推到國難五金睇到！！！"},{"pid":"80f53bc5eb91bff0d921d1496e1e944edca410d3","tid":1537822,"uid":146535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T05:26:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"40a672717e3041e5b8a637aa0de00e1aacdf1667","tid":1537822,"uid":69503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T05:26:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange